name: Design System-ish
description:
Here's a little copy of my design system I created a while ago. Feel free to build upon it and change things as needed. It was still a work in progress, and has been updated further beyond this though. Things like the color scheme will definitely have to change, but hey, duplicate and remix away.

PS: There are interactive components here, so if you are outside the beta testers, you won't be able to see those interactions in the prototype mode.
